# STLC Backlog Management Spec

## Overview
Software Testing Life Cycle (STLC) backlog management system for tracking user stories and bugs through the testing lifecycle.

## Requirements

### User Stories Management
- Create/edit/delete user stories
- Fields: Title, Description, Acceptance Criteria, Story Points, Priority, Epic, Status
- AI-powered generation from raw notes
- Kanban board view
- List view with sorting/filtering
- Drag-and-drop status updates

### Bug Tracking
- Create/edit/delete bugs
- Fields: Title, Description, Steps to Reproduce, Severity, Priority, Environment, Status
- AI-powered generation from raw notes
- Kanban board view
- List view with filtering
- Status workflow tracking

### Views
- **Kanban Board**: Visual workflow with columns for each status
- **List View**: Tabular display with all fields
- Toggle between views
- Search functionality
- Export to JSON/CSV

### Status Workflow
- New → Active → In Progress → Testing → Done → Closed
- Drag-and-drop status changes in Kanban
- Status dropdown in List view

### AI Generation
- Paste raw notes or descriptions
- AI generates structured user story or bug report
- Pre-fills all fields intelligently
- User can edit before saving

## Technical Implementation

### Data Models

**User Story**
```javascript
{
  id: string,
  title: string,
  description: string,
  acceptanceCriteria: string,
  storyPoints: number,
  priority: 'Critical' | 'High' | 'Medium' | 'Low',
  epic: string,
  status: string,
  createdAt: timestamp
}
```

**Bug**
```javascript
{
  id: string,
  title: string,
  description: string,
  stepsToReproduce: Array<{step: number, description: string}>,
  severity: 'Critical' | 'Major' | 'Minor' | 'Trivial',
  priority: 'Critical' | 'High' | 'Medium' | 'Low',
  environment: string,
  status: string,
  createdAt: timestamp
}
```

### API Endpoints
```javascript
POST /api/generate-from-notes
Body: { notes: string, type: 'story' | 'bug' }
Response: { generated: Object }
```

### Context Actions
- ADD_USER_STORY
- UPDATE_USER_STORY
- DELETE_USER_STORY
- ADD_BUG
- UPDATE_BUG
- DELETE_BUG

## User Flows

### Create User Story
1. Click "+ User Story" button
2. Enter details manually OR paste raw notes
3. If using AI: Click "Generate" to auto-fill fields
4. Review and edit generated content
5. Click "Save"
6. Story appears in Kanban/List view

### Track Bug
1. Click "+ Bug" button
2. Enter bug details or paste raw notes
3. AI generates structured bug report
4. Add steps to reproduce
5. Set severity and priority
6. Save to backlog
7. Track through workflow

### Kanban Workflow
1. View items organized by status columns
2. Drag item to new status column
3. Status updates automatically
4. Visual progress tracking

## Success Criteria
- Create story/bug in under 30 seconds
- AI generation accuracy > 85%
- Smooth drag-and-drop with no lag
- Support 1000+ items without performance issues
- Export complete data without loss
